data.title: Acoustic Guitars
data.meta_description: 518 W. Northern Ave., Pueblo, CO 81004 - Get top-grade acoustic, electric and acoustic-electric guitars at Elledge Music Inc. We make custom guitars too.
data.text:
Get Quality Guitars From Top Brands

You're sure to find the right guitar to suit your tastes, from one-of-a-kind Fireweed guitars to instruments from top brands like Oscar Schmidt, Washburn, and Teton.

Stop by today and let our experienced staff help direct you to the right fit for your playing style. We are backed by 57 years of musical sales experience. No matter what you pick, you're guaranteed a great price with our minimum advertised pricing!

Best of all, we're here for you during every step of your musical journey. In-store lessons are available. We have a wide variety of post-sale services, including instrument repairs and accessory recommendations.
